trans-unit.source: To explore Unix system performance metrics in <link><linkText>Application Insights</linkText><title></title></link>, install <link><linkText>collectd</linkText><title></title></link>, together with its Application Insights plug-in.
trans-unit.target: To explore Unix system performance metrics in <link><linkText>Application Insights</linkText><title></title></link>, install <link><linkText>collectd</linkText><title></title></link>, together with its Application Insights plug-in.

trans-unit.source: This open-source solution gathers a variety of system and network statistics.
trans-unit.target: This open-source solution gathers a variety of system and network statistics.

trans-unit.source: Typically you'll use collectd if you have already <link><linkText>instrumented your Java web service with Application Insights[java]</linkText><title></title></link>, so that you have more data to help you to enhance your app's performance or diagnose problems.
trans-unit.target: Typically you'll use collectd if you have already <link><linkText>instrumented your Java web service with Application Insights[java]</linkText><title></title></link>, so that you have more data to help you to enhance your app's performance or diagnose problems.

trans-unit.source: In your Application Insights resource, open <link><linkText>Metrics Explorer and add charts[metrics]</linkText><title></title></link>, selecting the metrics you want to see from the Custom category.
trans-unit.target: In your Application Insights resource, open <link><linkText>Metrics Explorer and add charts[metrics]</linkText><title></title></link>, selecting the metrics you want to see from the Custom category.

trans-unit.source: By default, the metrics are aggregated across all host machines from which the metrics were collected.
trans-unit.target: By default, the metrics are aggregated across all host machines from which the metrics were collected.

trans-unit.source: To view the metrics per host, in the Chart details blade, turn on Grouping and then choose to group by CollectD-Host.
trans-unit.target: To view the metrics per host, in the Chart details blade, turn on Grouping and then choose to group by CollectD-Host.
